  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to demonstrate correlation of the H/M ratio of AdreView when
      derived from a large field of view Anger SPECT system and from a small field of view high
      sensitivity (CZT) SPECT system.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
